require ecc;
function public callable void printsummary(readable int:32 chinese, readable int:32 math, readable int:32 english) code size 1024 max stack size 256 requires security level 1 allowed roles viewer {
    proceed verifyfunctionidentity();
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 total = compute ((chinese + math) + english) with overflow trap;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出系统标题" with justification "标题" with arguments { value by value = literal "成绩管理系统" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出标题" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出学生姓名" with justification "学生" with arguments { value by value = literal "学生：张三" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出学生" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出语文分数标签" with justification "语文标签" with arguments { value by value = literal "语文" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出语文标签" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of outputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出语文分数" with justification "语文分数" with arguments { value by value = chinese } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出语文分数" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出数学分数标签" with justification "数学标签" with arguments { value by value = literal "数学" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出数学标签" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of outputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出数学分数" with justification "数学分数" with arguments { value by value = math } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出数学分数" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出英语分数标签" with justification "英语标签" with arguments { value by value = literal "英语" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出英语标签" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of outputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出英语分数" with justification "英语分数" with arguments { value by value = english } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出英语分数" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出总分标签" with justification "总分标签" with arguments { value by value = literal "总分如下" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出总分标签" with approval timeout 1000;
    authorize invocation of outputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出总分" with justification "总分数字" with arguments { value by value = total } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出总分" with approval timeout 1000;
    if (total >= 270) judging authorized by root because literal "教务处授权本函数判断优秀等级" expects elseifs 1 else 1 {
        proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出优秀等级" with justification "优秀等级" with arguments { value by value = literal "等级：优秀" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出优秀等级" with approval timeout 1000;
    } else if (total >= 240) judging authorized by root because literal "教务处授权本函数判断良好等级" expects elseifs 0 else 1 {
        proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出良好等级" with justification "良好等级" with arguments { value by value = literal "等级：良好" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出良好等级" with approval timeout 1000;
    } else judging authorized by root because literal "教务处授权本函数进入补考兜底分支" {
        proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "查看成绩需要输出补考等级" with justification "补考等级" with arguments { value by value = literal "等级：需要补考" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain viewer with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出补考等级" with approval timeout 1000;
    }
}
function public callable void setscore(readable writable ptr<readable writable, int:32> target, readable int:32 value) code size 128 max stack size 64 requires security level 1 allowed roles editor {
    proceed verifyfunctionidentity();
    assign *target = value;
}
function public callable returnable void main() code size 8192 max stack size 512 requires security level 1 allowed roles admin {
    proceed verifyfunctionidentity();
    grant viewer to student via root;
    grant viewer to teacher via root;
    grant editor to teacher via root;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 chinese = 92;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 math = 88;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 english = 90;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 command = 1;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local int:32 newscore = 0;
    declare mutable readable writable purpose computational scope local bool:1 running = true;
    while (running == true) {
        proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "菜单循环需要输出功能列表" with justification "菜单标题" with arguments { value by value = literal "菜单：1学生查看 2改语文 3改数学 4改英语 5教师查看 0退出" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出菜单" with approval timeout 1000;
        authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "菜单循环需要提示输入命令" with justification "命令提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "请输入命令编号" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出命令提示" with approval timeout 1000;
        assign command = authorize invocation of inputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "菜单循环需要读取命令编号" with justification "读取命令" with arguments { } predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意读取命令" with approval timeout 1000;
        if (command == 0) judging authorized by root because literal "退出命令需要被明确判断" expects elseifs 0 else 1 {
            proceed assign running = false;
        } else judging authorized by root because literal "非退出命令需要继续分派权限函数" {
            proceed if (command == 1) judging authorized by root because literal "学生查看命令需要调用viewer权限函数" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of printsummary at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "学生查看成绩会触发输出" with justification "学生查看" with arguments { chinese by value = chinese, math by value = math, english by value = english } discarding return predictstackdepth 16 with authority chain student with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意学生查看" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
            if (command == 2) judging authorized by root because literal "修改语文命令需要editor权限" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改语文前需要提示输入新分数" with justification "语文输入提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "请输入新的语文成绩" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出语文输入提示" with approval timeout 1000;
                assign newscore = authorize invocation of inputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改语文需要读取新分数" with justification "读取语文" with arguments { } predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意读取语文" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of setscore at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with justification "教师修改语文" with arguments { target by reference = &chinese, value by value = newscore } discarding return predictstackdepth 8 with authority chain teacher with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意教师修改语文" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改语文后需要输出确认" with justification "语文修改确认" with arguments { value by value = literal "语文成绩已修改" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出语文确认" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
            if (command == 3) judging authorized by root because literal "修改数学命令需要editor权限" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改数学前需要提示输入新分数" with justification "数学输入提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "请输入新的数学成绩" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出数学输入提示" with approval timeout 1000;
                assign newscore = authorize invocation of inputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改数学需要读取新分数" with justification "读取数学" with arguments { } predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意读取数学" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of setscore at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with justification "教师修改数学" with arguments { target by reference = &math, value by value = newscore } discarding return predictstackdepth 8 with authority chain teacher with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意教师修改数学" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改数学后需要输出确认" with justification "数学修改确认" with arguments { value by value = literal "数学成绩已修改" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出数学确认" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
            if (command == 4) judging authorized by root because literal "修改英语命令需要editor权限" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改英语前需要提示输入新分数" with justification "英语输入提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "请输入新的英语成绩" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出英语输入提示" with approval timeout 1000;
                assign newscore = authorize invocation of inputint at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改英语需要读取新分数" with justification "读取英语" with arguments { } predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意读取英语" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of setscore at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with justification "教师修改英语" with arguments { target by reference = &english, value by value = newscore } discarding return predictstackdepth 8 with authority chain teacher with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意教师修改英语" with approval timeout 1000;
                authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "修改英语后需要输出确认" with justification "英语修改确认" with arguments { value by value = literal "英语成绩已修改" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出英语确认" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
            if (command == 5) judging authorized by root because literal "教师查看命令需要调用viewer权限函数" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of printsummary at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "教师查看成绩会触发输出" with justification "教师查看" with arguments { chinese by value = chinese, math by value = math, english by value = english } discarding return predictstackdepth 16 with authority chain teacher with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意教师查看" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
            if (command > 5) judging authorized by root because literal "非法命令需要被明确拒绝" expects elseifs 0 else 0 {
                proceed authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "非法命令需要输出错误信息" with justification "非法命令提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "命令无效" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出非法命令提示" with approval timeout 1000;
            }
        }
    }
    authorize invocation of println at security level 1 with memory limit 128 with timeout 1000 with io operation because literal "退出系统需要输出结束信息" with justification "退出提示" with arguments { value by value = literal "成绩管理系统已退出" } discarding return predictstackdepth 4 with authority chain admin with approval of alwaysapprove with approval justification "同意输出退出提示" with approval timeout 1000;
}
